How-how long?

18:12.300 --> 18:13.401
Wha... wha...

18:13.435 --> 18:15.136
Okay, wait for me. I...

18:15.170 --> 18:16.971
- Oh, my God.
- No, no, no. Just try to wait.

18:17.005 --> 18:18.239
Uh...
Is she... right now?

18:18.273 --> 18:19.573
- Her water just broke.
- Go! Go!

18:19.608 --> 18:21.142
- Oh, my God! Oh, my God,
- I have to get back to Ohio.

18:21.176 --> 18:23.711
- Oh, my God!
- I love you. I love you. Break a leg.

