♪ Little ♪

27:49.519 --> 27:53.089
♪ By my loving you ♪

27:53.123 --> 27:58.794
♪ Too much? ♪

27:58.829 --> 28:05.134
SUE and RACHEL:
♪ How is the view? ♪

28:05.168 --> 28:11.407
♪ Sunny and green? ♪

28:11.441 --> 28:16.679
♪ How do you compare it to ♪

28:16.713 --> 28:24.053
♪ The views you've seen? ♪

28:24.087 --> 28:30.393
♪ I know I am ♪

28:30.427 --> 28:33.396
♪ Better ♪

28:33.430 --> 28:36.065
♪ Braver ♪

28:36.099 --> 28:40.202
♪ And surer, too ♪

28:40.237 --> 28:46.208
♪ But you ♪

28:46.243 --> 28:52.348
♪ Are you now ♪

28:52.382 --> 28:58.020
♪ Who are you now? ♪

28:58.055 --> 29:04.827
♪ Are you someone ♪

29:04.861 --> 29:07.830
♪ Better ♪

29:09.766 --> 29:10.446
♪ For my ♪

29:15.305 --> 29:15.917
♪ Love? ♪

29:28.785 --> 29:30.920
(applause)

29:39.269 --> 29:40.870
Oh, my God. Oh,

29:40.904 --> 29:42.705
- I am gonna have a big glass of that.
- Yay.

29:42.739 --> 29:45.374
- Oh, my God, Rachel. You were so great.
- Thank you.

29:45.409 --> 29:47.476
I bawled during "Who Are You Now?".

29:47.479 --> 29:49.445
I had to blow my nose on Sam's sleeve.

29:49.479 --> 29:50.446
This is suede.

29:50.480 --> 29:51.514
I'm sorry. You guys,

29:51.548 --> 29:52.869
I love you so much.
I seriously...

29:52.883 --> 29:54.383
I couldn't have done this
without all of you.

29:54.418 --> 29:56.138
KURT: And you got flowers
from Quinn I know.

29:56.153 --> 29:58.721
And Artie and Mike Chang
and Puck and Principal Figgins.

29:58.755 --> 30:00.590
Clearly you're loved by many.

30:00.624 --> 30:02.325
(laughing)

30:03.493 --> 30:05.094
Whoa...
(whooping)

30:05.095 --> 30:06.329
Tonight,

30:06.363 --> 30:08.197
you are a star.

30:08.231 --> 30:10.733
(cheering)
Oh, my God. Thank you so much.

30:10.767 --> 30:13.002
You know what, you guys,
let's save all the praises

30:13.036 --> 30:15.071
- until after the <i> New York Times
</i> review comes out. - Yeah, yeah.

30:15.105 --> 30:16.472
- You're right, you're right.
- Yeah.

30:16.506 --> 30:18.140
We have, uh, six hours
of innocence left.

30:18.175 --> 30:21.310
- Whew. - And then when the reviews
hit the stand, we'll find out

30:21.345 --> 30:25.114
if we're the best thing
since sliced bread or toast.

30:25.148 --> 30:26.115
But...

30:26.149 --> 30:27.583
we are going

30:27.618 --> 30:29.151
- to celebrate tonight.
- Okay.

30:29.186 --> 30:32.021
We are going to have
an opening night party,

30:32.055 --> 30:34.490
Elio's restaurant,
Italian restaurant.

30:34.524 --> 30:36.726
Eggplant parmigiana

30:36.760 --> 30:39.595
always, always
brings me good luck.

30:39.630 --> 30:41.998
- Yeah! Yay.
- Rachel, Rachel,

30:42.032 --> 30:44.533
- your friends, huh?
- Yeah.

30:44.568 --> 30:46.602
- Bring everybody!
- (cheering)

30:46.637 --> 30:48.271
All right, bye.

30:48.305 --> 30:49.472
Whoa. Eggplant parmigiana?
Thank you.

30:49.506 --> 30:51.874
I can't believe it,
a real Broadway cast party.

30:51.909 --> 30:54.710
I don't really feel
like going to the party.

30:54.745 --> 30:56.279
I think that they're just gonna

30:56.313 --> 30:57.613
only be talking about the play,

30:57.648 --> 30:59.115
and... I don't know...
I'd rather just...

30:59.149 --> 31:00.449
celebrate with you guys.

31:00.484 --> 31:01.550
BLAINE:
I know just the place

31:01.585 --> 31:02.551
down in Greenwich Village.

31:02.586 --> 31:03.452
Trust me, Rachel,

31:03.487 --> 31:04.887
they're gonna love you there.

31:04.922 --> 31:07.023
(booming dance music playing)

31:13.130 --> 31:15.298
(laughing):
Oh, my God.

31:15.332 --> 31:16.632
Oh, my God.

31:16.667 --> 31:18.935
Rachel Berry?!
Here?!

31:18.969 --> 31:21.270
Oh, my God, you recognize me?

31:21.305 --> 31:24.207
(music stops) We've been
tracking <i> Funny Girl</i> for weeks.

31:24.241 --> 31:25.074
How was tonight?

31:25.108 --> 31:26.209
She was incredible.

31:26.243 --> 31:27.610
Oh, well, then
this is historic.

31:27.644 --> 31:30.046
You have to sing something...
it's Broadway tradition.

31:30.080 --> 31:32.248
- Oh, no. I'm... I'm not sure.
- Whatever the review

31:32.282 --> 31:34.717
says tomorrow, let's just love
and celebrate you tonight,

31:34.751 --> 31:35.952
right now.

31:35.986 --> 31:38.087
Well, in that case...

31:38.121 --> 31:40.041
- I'm here for the night!
- (cheering)

31:40.057 --> 31:41.157
Hit it!

31:41.191 --> 31:43.392
(NONONO's "Pumpin' Blood" begins)

31:49.433 --> 31:51.400
(whistling)

