won't break our bones ♪

32:16.360 --> 32:18.728
♪ We're in a car ♪

32:18.762 --> 32:21.130
♪ On the highway ♪

32:21.164 --> 32:24.000
♪ It's a magical feeling ♪

32:24.034 --> 32:27.303
♪ That no one's got a hold ♪

32:29.306 --> 32:31.607
♪ You're a catalyst ♪

32:31.642 --> 32:36.012
♪ To your happiness, you know ♪

32:36.046 --> 32:38.848
♪ 'Cause it's your heart ♪

